1 AN ACT concerning
2 Vehicle Laws – Speed Monitoring Systems – Residential Districts
3 FOR the purpose of establishing that certain provisions of law authorizing the use of speed
4 monitoring systems in certain residential districts apply statewide; requiring all
5 speed limit signs on certain highways in residential districts to include certain signs;
6 and generally relating to speed monitoring systems in residential districts.
